-- LSE offers 4.9 shares for each Borsa share: source
-- 
-- Fri Jun 22, 2007 10:41am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/06/22/us-borsa-takeover-shares-idUSMAT00695620070622

 

 MILAN  (Reuters) - The London Stock Exchange ( LSE.L ) is offering 4.9 of its shares for every Borsa Italiana share in its bid for the Milan bourse, a source close to the situation said on Friday. 

 The source said the deal could close in three to four months, definitely within the year.